rows.label: bf04090100_0010
rows.name:
Right, so it looks like
we're heading out tomorrow.

rows.label: bf04090100_0020
rows.name:
Everyone, make sure
you're ready by then!

rows.label: bf04090100_0060
rows.name:
You can find quality goods here from
all around Alst. You like the place?

rows.label: bf04090100_0070
rows.name:
Yes. If there's time before we leave,
I think I'll have another cup later.

rows.label: bf04090100_0080
rows.name:
Mmmm, feels so good to rest in a
proper inn after a long voyage!

rows.label: bf04090100_0090
rows.name: Yeah. It's good to be on familiar shores again.
